content: I'm looking to restock my pantry and fridge with some essentials. I just used up the last of my frozen peas and carrots, and I think I need to get some more of those. Do you have any recommendations for other healthy staples I should consider picking up? By the way, I recently made a big batch of vegetable stir-fry on Sunday evening, which lasted me until Tuesday, so I'm all set on veggies for now.
